snippet: The first of a dozen defendants in the hazing death of a Florida A&M drum major entered a plea of no contest to third-degree felony hazing on Tuesday.
abstract: Brian Jones, first of a dozen defendants in the hazing death of Florida A&M drum major Robert Champion, enters plea of no contest to third-degree felony hazing.
lead_paragraph: The first of a dozen defendants in the hazing death of a Florida A&M drum major entered a plea of no contest to third-degree felony hazing on Tuesday.
